#. type: delimited block =
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/core/aop/ataspectj/advice.adoc:628
msgid ""
"Spring AOP can handle generics used in class declarations and method "
"parameters. Suppose you have a generic type like the following:"
