#. type: delimited block =
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/core/aop/ataspectj/advice.adoc:654
msgid ""
"You can restrict interception of method types to certain parameter types by "
"tying the advice parameter to the parameter type for which you want to "
